🍉️1. Creating the database.
  --> create database expy;	(Note: expy is database name) 

🍉️2.Connecting the database.
  --> \c expy		(Note: expy is the database name)

🍉️3.Connecting the default database.
  --> \c postgres	

🍉️4.Deleting the database.
  --> drop database expy

🍉️5.Exiting the postgres shell.
  -->\q

